Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.14,0:08:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是随便的话 稍后就会滑溜溜的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.85,0:08:07.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这个意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.94,0:08:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说呢 总觉得KISS也很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:11.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.20,0:08:14.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊  你是说这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.77,0:08:17.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  说的是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.63,0:08:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KISS  昨天悠二的感觉也很怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.39,0:08:43.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教我的并没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.78,0:08:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.15,0:08:50.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 原来在这啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.90,0:08:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在查什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:54.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.63,0:08:56.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.49,0:08:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 也不是什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.30,0:09:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心也没问题的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.88,0:09:10.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,池同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.16,0:09:14.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才也说了吧 只是和平井同学关系好而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.51,0:09:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没恋爱的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.06,0:09:20.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.86,0:09:21.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:25.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐 我们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.06,0:09:27.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的状态如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.02,0:09:30.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是  少罗嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:32.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头会嗡嗡响的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.44,0:09:35.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 荣太 脸上的伤是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.66,0:09:39.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  这个是给球打了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.99,0:09:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,启作 荣太
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:45.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉酒也腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.59,0:09:51.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（你搞什么  你搞什么是在搞什么）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.38,0:09:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KISS到底有什么意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.13,0:09:57.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 但为什么问这种问题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.76,0:09:58.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.73,0:10:02.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看似简单却很难回答的问题呢  小夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.01,0:10:04.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然你说去查过了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.81,0:10:05.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.08,0:10:10.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算去图书馆查书 也只查到以前知道的那些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.82,0:10:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样的做法是知道 也看过别人做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.47,0:10:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.29,0:10:20.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感到别人认为的意思和我所知道的意思好像完全不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.29,0:10:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想千草的话一定知道这个的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.67,0:10:27.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小说或文学之类的读过没
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.69,0:10:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为阿拉斯拖鲁说过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加入个人主观的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.72,0:10:35.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对恰当的分析理性的思索毫无作用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.29,0:10:41.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿拉斯拖鲁先生好像是在远方代替父亲的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有很了不起的见解呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.86,0:10:44.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.99,0:10:46.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.84,0:10:49.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是呢  小夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.23,0:11:03.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是呢  小夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:07.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种时候 这样说反而不能理解呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:14.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,资料上所记载的只有现存的事实而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.17,0:11:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但小夏娜所考虑的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.38,0:11:18.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却是这以外的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:22.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说模模糊糊没有完整的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.65,0:11:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 是关于心和感情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.46,0:11:26.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心和感情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.52,0:11:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该知道身体的相互接触是深爱之情的表现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.73,0:11:36.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 KISS也是其中一种吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.23,0:11:39.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,握手和拥抱之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.45,0:11:40.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.87,0:11:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是这样没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.00,0:11:48.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好 比如和阿拉斯拖鲁先生这么做的话没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.12,0:11:49.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.00,0:11:50.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那和小悠能做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.17,0:11:56.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这  这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.54,0:12:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重新想一下的话 也挺不好意思的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.85,0:12:01.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.26,0:12:04.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是所说内容的中心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.80,0:12:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且说是KISS
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.88,0:12:10.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲脸颊和嘴对嘴的意思可完全不一样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和  和悠二嘴对嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.36,0:12:19.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不要这样 不想被亲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.08,0:12:22.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.77,0:12:23.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千草
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.18,0:12:25.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能被亲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.83,0:12:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就算是阿拉斯拖鲁先生也不能做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.54,0:12:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.86,0:12:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我呢 是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘴对嘴的KISS 是像发誓一样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.91,0:12:39.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.55,0:12:43.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 用自己的全部来发誓也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.26,0:12:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把自己的全部托付出去也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.64,0:12:47.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种发誓的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.82,0:12:49.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是KISS
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.95,0:13:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚就到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.32,0:13:08.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点累了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.04,0:13:13.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.54,0:13:14.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.59,0:13:15.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托零时迷子的福
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.22,0:13:19.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的力量每到零点就会恢复吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.22,0:13:21.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:24.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  就是指不会变老吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.81,0:13:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己去确认如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.93,0:13:29.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然可能会花很长时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.97,0:13:30.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.21,0:13:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会和夏娜永远在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.90,0:13:44.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:45.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.74,0:13:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有件事要拜托你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.83,0:14:00.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.42,0:14:02.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.93,0:14:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千草 借下电话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.22,0:14:06.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.26,0:14:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但小夏娜 到去学校的时间了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.44,0:14:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.85,0:14:13.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.31,0:14:16.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.32,0:14:18.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千草
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.43,0:14:19.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换人接了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.77,0:14:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.86,0:14:26.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.88,0:14:29.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次通话 夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.46,0:14:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下的名字是阿拉斯拖鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.56,0:14:35.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 原来是阿拉斯拖鲁先生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.12,0:14:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平井紫总是承蒙您照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.29,0:14:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是坂井悠二的母亲 名叫千草
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.25,0:14:48.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才是 给您添了不少麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.83,0:14:50.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那特地来联系究竟有何贵干呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.85,0:14:59.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是平井紫的事 请直说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.72,0:15:05.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 啊  还有那个请称之为夏娜就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:07.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是这么叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 阿拉斯拖鲁先生也公认了的昵称呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:14.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:17.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  我想说的是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.21,0:15:18.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.24,0:15:21.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实 是昨天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:22.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.06,0:15:27.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.12,0:15:29.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠小夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.40,0:15:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去学校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.14,0:15:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.52,0:15:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:38.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.27,0:15:41.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.93,0:15:46.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是否定夫人的恋爱观
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.81,0:15:50.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像昨天的那些话请不要说了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.09,0:15:53.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏娜说出去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.44,0:15:56.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是我硬逼着她说出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.09,0:16:01.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论何时 能听到那个小夏娜说这些的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.59,0:16:05.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是被深深信赖着的证据呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.68,0:16:06.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.19,0:16:10.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来小夏娜是被很重视地抚养长大的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.65,0:16:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是非常单纯的好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.73,0:16:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.02,0:16:15.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.42,0:16:22.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会诱发夏娜像昨天一样和坂井悠二欠考虑的接触的发言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.91,0:16:24.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请尽量小心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.28,0:16:27.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的意思我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.51,0:16:30.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夫人非常明白事理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.58,0:16:33.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来就能全交给您了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.15,0:16:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.78,0:16:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.78,0:16:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了小夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:40.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以再和您谈谈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.13,0:16:42.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.75,0:16:44.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏娜和说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个高贵而又厉害的好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.41,0:16:53.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我以为在另一方面却有着非常幼小而脆弱的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.01,0:16:58.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请继续
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.92,0:17:01.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 那失礼的说一句
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.23,0:17:09.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感到小夏娜对人的感情和心都很陌生 有着毫无防备之处
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.15,0:17:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我家的悠二是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.01,0:17:15.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,困扰年轻人的东西出现时
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.20,0:17:19.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那纯真无垢的孩子会多么抵触呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.41,0:17:23.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天我感觉到了这危险
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.67,0:17:25.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才说了那些话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.07,0:17:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是  还太早了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.35,0:17:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想花上数年时间 让她经历各种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.34,0:17:37.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后慢慢地告诉她会比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.89,0:17:41.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦不会由我们随心所欲地发生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.47,0:17:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:46.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我想教她应该教的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.33,0:17:49.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不会有太早这说法的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也为了小夏娜自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.23,0:17:59.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且女孩子可是比外观看起来早熟很多的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.04,0:18:03.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.40,0:18:05.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.64,0:18:10.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前所做的不适当的发言可以撤回么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.09,0:18:12.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.11,0:18:14.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说了大言不惭的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.55,0:18:16.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏娜的话没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.82,0:18:18.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要好好教她的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:23.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就应该会从内心找到属于自己的做法和正确答案的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.02,0:18:25.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种信赖应该有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.12,0:18:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.73,0:18:39.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.03,0:18:42.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近了 好近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.87,0:18:46.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.63,0:18:48.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像在找什么东西似的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.92,0:18:49.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.23,0:18:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 不愧是索拉特的「欲望的嗅觉」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.16,0:18:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种令人厌烦的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.98,0:18:57.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是火焰之雾了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.89,0:18:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 哪里哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.62,0:19:00.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.56,0:19:02.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火焰之雾 好想要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.98,0:19:04.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.77,0:19:07.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多要给察觉到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:09.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该明白火焰之雾的出现只是时间问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.12,0:19:16.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那  打算如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.36,0:19:20.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再设些机关 以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.78,0:19:24.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始吧 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:25.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.40,0:19:29.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一步 先去打个招呼如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.15,0:19:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为要找出来  是很简单的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.86,0:19:42.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.48,0:19:46.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 刚才阿拉斯拖鲁在电话里说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.34,0:19:48.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天的事怎么怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.93,0:19:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.87,0:19:54.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.56,0:19:55.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.52,0:19:58.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你绝对绝对不做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.62,0:20:03.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.53,0:20:07.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的话 做了坂井同学的份
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.90,0:20:09.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.26,0:20:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为一直都吃饭团
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.12,0:20:14.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.04,0:20:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.34,0:20:18.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.24,0:20:20.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.84,0:20:21.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从哪个开始吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.06,0:20:28.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真伤脑筋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.08,0:20:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀  买了不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.13,0:20:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岂止「不少」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:45.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:47.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,购物才刚开始啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.62,0:20:59.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是在青黄不接时又来了大客户
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.02,0:21:01.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.31,0:21:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.74,0:21:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美丽的杀戮者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:17.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种地方干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.75,0:21:19.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠不住的色男
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.82,0:21:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 认识的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.62,0:21:24.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 给你介绍一下 泰莉亚露
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.99,0:21:27.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在火焰之雾里也屈指可数的杀手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.36,0:21:31.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悼词的咏唱者——玛丘莉·顿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.83,0:21:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那蹂躏的爪牙就
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.02,0:21:35.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.06,0:21:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这些人没拿着我想要的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.39,0:21:40.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.35,0:21:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为很简单就能找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.39,0:21:45.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却不是猎物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.68,0:21:47.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 所以走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.90,0:21:49.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥既然说了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.33,0:21:55.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙不是红世之徒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.40,0:21:57.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放过他们没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.61,0:22:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不是放过他们哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.99,0:22:02.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是被放过了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.79,0:22:05.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴 傻瓜丸子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.70,0:22:14.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那以后和老妈说了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.89,0:22:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没必要在意
