Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.28,0:22:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个 加紧锻炼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.29,0:22:23.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让母亲蒙羞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.92,0:22:25.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.77,0:22:29.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠小夏娜 饭准备好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.84,0:22:30.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
